<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/concerned-citizens-in-cancer-alley-vow-to-ramp-up-battle-against-industrial-pollution-in-2018/">Concerned Citizens in Cancer Alley Vow to Ramp Up Battle Against Industrial Pollution in 2018</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">A group of residents group plans to get political and broaden its reach.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/julie-dermansky/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Julie Dermansky</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://www.desmogblog.com/2018/01/04/concerned-citizens-st-john-louisiana-cancer-alley-pollution-fight' itemprop='url'>DeSmogBlog</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2018-01-10T05:00:00+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2018-01-10T05:00:00+00:00">January 10, 2018</time>
<div class="hide" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
<a href="https://truthout.org" itemprop="url">
<span itemprop="name">
Truthout
</span>
</a>
